<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Parkland </h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Established in 1974, the community in Parkland continues to offer a great quality of
                living at a reasonable value. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">The Parkland Real Estate forms a small community that offers easy access to an array of
                amenities such as shopping complexes, schools, restaurants, cafes, recreational venues and public
                transportation systems. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Parkland comprise majorly single-family detached and attached units that
                are often listed within a price range of around $400,000 up to around the mid 800s.</p>
        </div>
